metadata.name: Deep delight- Magenta 1
metadata.description:
Flowers are always a symbol of harmony, love, and beauty and are the best messenger of kindness and peace. 
In this collection, I painted gorgeous flowers in a modern way as a memo of friendship. They are presented with some variations in pattern and different colors. So, everyone can find one that she/he loves. 
The first phase of this collection includes 4 pieces. Other phases will come later with gradual price increase in each phase. Differences in flower patterns will be done in coming works. 
Hope you feel the love hidden in these nice flowers. Letâ€™s begin our friendship.
